| invo_id | pr_id | quantity |
+---------+-------+----------+
|     101 |     1 |        2 |
|     102 |     2 |        1 |
|     104 |     4 |        1 |
|     105 |     5 |        4 |
|     103 |     3 |        1 |
|     103 |     1 |        3 |
+---------+-------+----------+
6 rows in set (0.04 sec)

mysql> UPDATE invoice_item SET quantity=3 where invo_id=101;
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.11 sec)
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1  Warnings: 0

